OL,3,CSummer Solstice 2026: Why June 21st is
OL,4,Cthe longest day of the year?
OL,6,FIt was not lived in and could not have
OL,7,Fbeen defended, so there must have been
OL,8,Fa spiritual reason why Neolithic and
OL,9,FBronze Age people put so much effort
OL,10,Finto building it.
OL,12,FMany theories have been put forward
OL,13,Fover the years, but no one truly knows.
OL,15,FMarking the movements of the sun was
OL,16,Fclearly important to the people who
OL,17,Fbuilt Stonehenge, as they went to such
OL,18,Fgreat lengths to align the monument
OL,19,Fwith them.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
