OL,3,CSummer Solstice 2026: Why June 21st is
OL,4,Cthe longest day of the year?
OL,6,FEnglish Heritage is urging visitors to
OL,7,Freport anything concerning, or to seek
OL,8,Fhelp from any of the security or
OL,9,Fstewarding team which will be on duty.
OL,11,FThe Wiltshire Police and the South
OL,12,FWestern Ambulance Service NHS Trust
OL,13,Fwill also be in attendance to ensure
OL,14,Fthe smooth running of Summer Solstice.
OL,16,FWhere can I watch the solstice?
OL,18,FIf you don't have a ticker for the
OL,19,Fevent, you can watch it on English
OL,20,FHeritage's live stream here!
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
